HEADWORD: Eximious
<hw>Ex*im"ious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>eximius</ets> taken out, <it>i. e.</it> select, fr.
<ets>eximere</ets> to take out. See <er>Exempt</er>.]</ety> <def>Select;
choice; hence, extraordinary, excellent.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>eximious</qex> and arcane science of physic.</q>
